      "text": "Thanks for volunteering for the open seat! That was amazing moment. And then for prepping the lightning talk while nobody else seemed to want to start. I can only say: Courage, courage!\n\nAnd as Šimon Kořený mentioned in his comment, your experiences were super valuable, as your journey is very unique (but to some extent relatable to many people I think) and I'm glad that we could hear your views and your story as well.\n\n(btw the rest of the panelists did get the questions in advance, but just a few hours in advance, and they were many, so they couldn't really prepare for it much either 😅 )",
